-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
# Synthetic placeholder for the e2e fixture. The crypto playbook reads
# attribute summaries from openssl x509 -text rather than reparsing the
# DER, so this fixture's value is the file's presence + the captured
# metadata in evidence.json (RSA-2048, 3-year validity, no PQC hybrid).
# Replacing this with a real certificate is not necessary for detection;
# the indicator fires on the metadata.
-----END CERTIFICATE-----
